# Env config is OPTIONAL — src/lib/supabase.ts routes to the right Supabase
# project automatically (production vs staging) based on VITE_APP_ENV, which the
# Vercel build sets from VERCEL_ENV. Local dev defaults to staging.
#
# Only set these to force a specific database (copy to .env.local):
VITE_SUPABASE_URL=https://your-project.supabase.co
VITE_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY=your-anon-publishable-key
